		<releaseNotes>This version of the Warehouse Management mobile app introduces the following fixes and improvements:
• Improved authentication for iOS.
• Fixed an issue where a toast message blocked scanning on iOS.
• Implemented new scrollable details card settings.  This option allows the details card to be scrolled, so you can view more information on one screen. The scrollable details card is designed for larger screens. On smaller devices, the feature may not work as expected. On smaller screens, switching to landscape mode may reduce the available space, which could affect scrollable behavior.
• Fixed an issue where the keyboard covered the bottom buttons on the Edit Connection page on iOS
• Fixed an issue that caused the error message to be displayed twice consecutively during blind cycle count.
• Fixed an issue that caused random animation crashes on older devices.
• Expanded device compatibility to allow more device types to install the app.
• Improved performance.
• Fix bug where step banner displayed the generic placeholder &quot;Scan or enter here&quot; instead of showing the value from the step.</releaseNotes>
